{"tid":682531,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔睇波判斷力>>>>>>名宿 教練 隊醫 沙拿本人","createTime":"2018-05-29T03:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T10:06:09.000Z","uid":12458,"like":27,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8093c555d0a3a47c0d92deec327b86304482ec66","tid":682531,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人唔笑 痢疤都吠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔洗提我 我去屌鮑姐先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c6e1c4104d26711ffc7a5e53490871f7ec9e1a","tid":682531,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b32c6391bae7e4b91e4503ba43dcc476e63474","tid":682531,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94c6e1c4104d26711ffc7a5e53490871f7ec9e1a","tid":682531,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0da0448304142bd579b63a82e616af8d12ad2d7","tid":682531,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:14:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27a1c8a7074b6d0a3098e51f6cc58daba2f3e35b","tid":682531,"uid":35176,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:16:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">里奧&middot;費迪南、林柏特：利物浦進不了聯賽前四</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2月2日訊<br />\n<br />\n前曼聯中衛里奧&middot;費迪南以及前車路士中場林柏特一致看好曼城、曼聯、車路士以及熱刺將成為本賽季英超聯賽前四名的球隊，他們都相信目前排名第三的利物浦將掉出前四行列。<br />\n<br />\n目前曼城在英超積分榜上一騎絕塵，他們以22勝2平1負的戰績積68分遙遙領先於身後的曼聯。這意味著除非發生奇蹟，否則其餘諸強只有三個歐冠席位可以爭取。紅魔以53分排名第二，利物浦與車路士同積50分，但紅軍以淨勝球優勢佔據第三，藍軍屈居第四，熱刺則以2分之差緊隨前四集團。阿仙奴目前則有些被甩開，他們落後熱刺有6分差距。<br />\n<br />\n對於本賽季聯賽前四的歸屬，林柏特以及里奧&middot;費迪南都有一致的看法。在被問到誰能獲得本賽季聯賽前四時，林柏特回答說：&ldquo;曼城、曼聯、車路士以及熱刺。利物浦防守的弱點依然沒有得到解決，他們在前場的實力很強，但他們還在冬窗失去了古天奴。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n而里奧-費迪南對此非常贊同，他說：&ldquo;我會選擇曼城、曼聯、熱刺，我還會選車路士。如果夏薩特能繼續這樣的表現並且保持健康，那麼他會帶領車路士進入前四。我認為利物浦會掉出前四位置，防守上，就像林柏特所說，他們不夠強。而他們在前場還是非常出色，很有觀賞性的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/rio-ferdinand-frank-lampard-both-11952627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Fnews%2Frio-ferdinand-frank-lampard-both-11952627&d=Ymjqb4qXfs%2FskuslA%2FANxC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=fd5385d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/rio-ferdinand-frank-lampard-both-11952627</a>"},{"pid":"60f96595e75d3dfaafde3fcc6597a2f6498e3812","tid":682531,"uid":168146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d097583b7cb3ecf2a1857ae96364787db573da1","tid":682531,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:32:05.000Z","msg":"名宿出名燈都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ebf027bc0628fd5e8fd06455e519a8c9af345f","tid":682531,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:41:39.000Z","msg":"自嘲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41d2adf8123092168c3a2ed64814d98091480d6","tid":6825