627&d=Ymjqb4qXfs%2FskuslA%2FANxC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=fd5385d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/rio-ferdinand-frank-lampard-both-11952627</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T09:58:27.000Z","msg":"何wayne估中晒前六排名都話拉膠冇問題喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4322c07127b9e23ffb5527db3c898eadecb50a7b","tid":682531,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:06:09.000Z","msg":"至於你信不信，反正我就是信了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}